PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR, namely the Hon. WILLIAM ARTHUR ESSON, Chief Justice of the Supreme Court of British Columbia, who shall temporarily execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of BRITISH COLUMBIA for the duration of the period extending from November 16 to November 19, 1993.
